data.description: Beautiful home in popular Elgin School District. This 3 BR 2 BA home has brand new carpet and a modern color scheme. It has a great kitchen with plenty of cabinets and counterspace that opens to a large living area. It has kitchen dining as well as formal dining areas. You're not formal? No problem! The formal dining area could easily convert to a home office or an extra sitting area. The primary bedroom is large enough to accommodate a king bed plus extra dressers. The primary bathroom has a jetted tub and separate shower, dual sinks and lots of counter space. Mother-in-law floor plan. This home has been lovingly cared for and it's just waiting for you to add your family photo over the fireplace. Call the Munchel Team to check it out. (580)574-0684.
